					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6050188#post-4399501</guid>
				<title>if i could +100 i would</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6050188/apotheosis-hub#post-4399501</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2019 00:26:24 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>lavenderbloodstains</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2615908</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>apotheosis is a phenomenal hub. it is such a memorable and compelling story that it now serves as one of my main inspirations and aspirations for my writing. it's been about a year since ive read the story but i can still remember many of the concepts and how uniquely they were presented vividly. the shape of a gun is one of my favorite tales on the site, and really exemplified for me the proper way to portray the embodiment of a concept.</p> <p>what i'm saying is, phenomenal work, and if i could upvote this hub a hundred times over, i would.</p> <p>+100</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
